description: Exports all the device identities in the IoT hub identity registry to an Azure Storage blob container. For more information, see: https://docs.microsoft.com/azure/iot-hub/iot-hub-devguide-identity-registry#import-and-export-device-identities.

excludekeys.description: The value indicating whether keys should be excluded during export.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group that contains the IoT hub.

resource_name.description: The name of the IoT hub.

export_devices_parameters.description: The parameters that specify the export devices operation.
